00:39:32.060 --> 00:39:40.299
Thomas Adler: do almost anything with an English major. And, you know, I always read a lot anyway, so,

329
00:39:40.840 --> 00:39:55.280
Thomas Adler: it was an easy thing to fall into as a major, you know, take literature classes, and some of Archie's classes, you know, were listed or cross-listed under literature fields, you know, it's,

