00:40:32.490 --> 00:40:51.979
Thomas Adler: But, you know, they were pretty pleased, you know, I think, anyway, that I'd gone on to graduate school in any form, you know, and my older brother, Peter, also did a graduate degree. He ended up, you know, he did a PhD in sociology.

336
00:40:52.130 --> 00:40:55.720
Thomas Adler: And, you know, has… so…

337
00:40:55.930 --> 00:41:02.309
Thomas Adler: You know, we've done okay, you know, and my, my parents.

