539
01:05:47.750 --> 01:05:48.920
Thomas Adler: So…

540
01:05:49.210 --> 01:06:01.370
Thomas Adler: what that meant for us was that, you know, we would see declining enrollments to our folklore classes. And and our folklore classes also did not

541
01:06:01.730 --> 01:06:04.980
