554
01:07:15.090 --> 01:07:22.759
Thomas Adler: then Jim Leary went up for tenure and also didn't make it. And that was a shock to me and

555
01:07:23.260 --> 01:07:36.870
Thomas Adler: to everyone who knew him, because he had published a good deal by then, and those of us who knew him could see that he was already within the field, and even nationally and internationally. He was a star, a rising star.

556
01:07:37.150 --> 01:07:41.459
Thomas Adler: And it was… it was like, what's… what's going on? If…

557
01:07:41.670 --> 01:07:48.770
