558
01:07:48.960 --> 01:07:50.750
Thomas Adler: And to give him tenure?

559
01:07:51.150 --> 01:07:52.620
Thomas Adler: Something's wrong.

560
01:07:53.050 --> 01:08:01.009
Thomas Adler: And I'd say largely as a consequence of that, I had some publications, but nothing sufficient, I thought.

561
01:08:01.210 --> 01:08:12.350
Thomas Adler: to get over that hurdle, so I didn't even try. I did not pursue a 10-year decision. So after 7 years, or 7 and a half years, whatever it was.

