01:08:23.290 --> 01:08:26.250
Thomas Adler: So, I looked around to see…

565
01:08:26.520 --> 01:08:30.709
Thomas Adler: what's next? What can I do? I had a neighbor

566
01:08:30.870 --> 01:08:40.589
Thomas Adler: As I say, I had worked with computers all my life, practically, since high school, and by this time, there were personal computers and so on.

567
01:08:40.750 --> 01:08:43.399
Thomas Adler: I had a neighbor who,

