584
01:10:23.560 --> 01:10:37.959
Thomas Adler: Which meant that I, for the most part, stayed in Lexington for the next few years, and worked with Harold and other support personnel. They had support people in other specific areas, people that worked with

585
01:10:37.960 --> 01:10:44.240
