591
01:11:35.640 --> 01:11:38.060
Thomas Adler: And, and, you know, he…

592
01:11:38.420 --> 01:11:46.969
Thomas Adler: Wood and I would travel around and do these things, whether it was in Ohio somewhere, or Nashville, Tennessee, or whatever, we'd do these seminars, and

593
01:11:47.260 --> 01:11:56.269
